@EndUserText.label: 'Outgoing Deliveries'
@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
@Metadata.ignorePropagatedAnnotations: true
@Metadata.allowExtensions: true
@ObjectModel.usageType:{
    serviceQuality: #X,
    sizeCategory: #S,
    dataClass: #MIXED
}
define root view entity zetr_ddl_p_outgoing_deliveries
  provider contract transactional_query
  as projection on zetr_ddl_i_outgoing_deliveries
{
  key     DocumentUUID,
          @ObjectModel.text.element: ['CompanyTitle']
          CompanyCode,
          CompanyTitle,
          DocumentNumber,
          FiscalYear,
          @ObjectModel.text.element: ['DocumentTypeText']
          DocumentType,
          DocumentTypeText,
          ObjectType,
          @ObjectModel.text.element: ['ReferenceDocumentTypeText']
          ReferenceDocumentType,
          ReferenceDocumentTypeText,
          Plant,
          StorageLocation,
          ReceivingPlant,
          ReceivingStorageLocation,
          BusinessArea,
          MovementType,
          SpecialStockIndicator,
          @ObjectModel.text.element: ['PartnerName']
          PartnerNumber,
          PartnerName,
          TaxID,
          Aliass,
          DocumentDate,
          ProfileID,
          DeliveryType,
          SerialPrefix,
          XSLTTemplate,
          Reversed,
          ReverseDate,
          Archived,
          PrintedDocumentNumber,
          PrintedDocumentDate,
          Printed,
          Sender,
          SendDate,
          SendTime,
          DeliveryIDSaved,
          CollectItems,
          @ObjectModel.text.element: ['StatusCodeText']
          StatusCode,
          StatusCodeText,
          ToBeSent,
          OverallStatus,
          StatusCriticality,
          StatusDetail,
          @ObjectModel.text.element: ['ResponseText']
          Response,
          ResponseText,
          ResponseUUID,
          @ObjectModel.text.element: ['ItemResponseText']
          ItemResponse,
          ItemResponseText,
          @ObjectModel.text.element: ['TRAStatusCodeText']
          TRAStatusCode,
          TRAStatusCodeText,
          Resendable,
          IntegratorDocumentID,
          EnvelopeUUID,
          DeliveryUUID,
          DeliveryID,
          DeliveryNote,
          @ObjectModel.text.element: ['CreatedByName']
          CreatedBy,
          CreatedByName,
          CreateDate,
          CreateTime,
          Preview,
          @ObjectModel.virtualElementCalculatedBy: 'ABAP:ZCL_ETR_OUTDLV_LIST_VIREL'
  virtual ContentURL         : abap.string(0),
          @ObjectModel.virtualElementCalculatedBy: 'ABAP:ZCL_ETR_OUTDLV_LIST_VIREL'
  virtual DocumentDisplayUrl : abap.string(0),
          @ObjectModel.virtualElementCalculatedBy: 'ABAP:ZCL_ETR_OUTDLV_LIST_VIREL'
  virtual ResponseContentUrl : abap.string(0),
          /* Associations */
          _deliveryContents        : redirected to composition child zetr_ddl_p_outgoing_delcont,
          _deliveryLogs            : redirected to composition child zetr_ddl_p_outgoing_dellogs,
          _deliveryTransporters    : redirected to composition child zetr_ddl_p_outgoing_deltrns,
          _deliveryTransportHeader : redirected to composition child zetr_ddl_p_outgoing_deltdat,
          _deliveryItems           : redirected to composition child zetr_ddl_p_outgoing_delitem
}
